author: Carly Stern At New York Fashion Week For Dailymail.Com
title: Kanye West shows Yeezy Season 5 at New York Fashion Week | Daily Mail Online
text: Soldiering on! Kanye West turns out a camouflage-packed runway for Yeezy Season 5 at his first New York Fashion Week show since his breakdown Kanye West debuted his Season 5 collection in New York City on Wednesday afternoon The new designs looked similar to those in past collections and were made up of mostly neutral hues Signs outside the venue warned attendees not to share images on social media His wife Kim Kardashian and sister-in-law Kylie Jenner were on hand to watch the show Kanye, who was hospitalized late last year, didn't come out to take a bow but remained backstage Published: 20:57 GMT, 15 February 2017 | Updated: 00:17 GMT, 16 February 2017 352 shares
